cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.LG

This paper discusses a network management algorithm for big data processing in IoT, specifically focusing on mobile-edge computing (MEC) network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization algorithms and data analysis, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The proposed algorithm aims to stabilize data processing delay and save energy, which could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
